## Living Design 3.5 Component Inventory

### Available Components (USE THESE!)

#### Buttons & Actions
- âś… `Button.tsx` - All button needs (primary, secondary, tertiary, destructive)
- âś… `ButtonGroup.tsx` - Multiple buttons layout
- âś… `IconButton.tsx` - Icon-only buttons (if available)

#### Data Display
- âś… `tag.tsx` - Status tags and labels
- âś… `olq-tag.tsx` - OLQ percentage badges
- âś… `badge.tsx` - Notification badges

#### Overlays
- âś… `popover.tsx` - Popovers with arrow support
- âś… `dialog.tsx` - Modal dialogs
- âś… `alert-dialog.tsx` - Confirmation dialogs

#### Forms
- âś… `select.tsx` - Dropdown selects
- âś… `input.tsx` - Text inputs
- âś… `checkbox.tsx` - Checkboxes
- âś… `calendar.tsx` - Date picker

#### Navigation
- âś… `Menu.tsx` - Dropdown menus

#### Panels & Drawers
- âś… **ALL panels MUST be resizable** - See `guidelines/Panel.md` for complete spec
- **REQUIRED**: Min width 420px, Max width 800px (or responsive)
- **REQUIRED**: Resize handle on left edge with visual indicator
- **REQUIRED**: localStorage persistence of user's preferred width
- **REQUIRED**: Responsive behavior for small screens

